HEADWORD: Paneulogism
<hw>Pan*eu"lo*gism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Pan-</er>, <er>Eulogy</er>.]</ety> <def>Eulogy of everything;
indiscriminate praise.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

